### Concept Work for Surface Table

# Future Health Care Concept

![Concept Work for Surface Table](../images/projects/6_3.png "Concept Work for Surface Table")

A concept project on the Microsoft Surface table, posing questions around the future of health care. This application lets users investigate their health data over time and it allows for comparisons between average situations and the users own data.

![Concept Work for Surface Table](../images/projects/6_2.png "Concept Work for Surface Table")

Working with a platform like Microsoft Surface raised a lot of interesting challenges, such as how do design applications for users standing around the table. The project experimented with the circular shape as a means to access the data from any direction.
